        "timestamp": "2018-08-15 20:36:36.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\nDiscussion with [~prioux] and [~pau2882] - In prep of working more with the AAI and LF/CIMAN teams - I will add some subtasks based on the experience [~pau2882] and I have gained (mostly Prudence) - on getting the repo in shape with jjb jobs - working with [~jwagantall] and [~jeremyphelps]\n\nraised separate parent epic for the devops work - LOG-609 containing the yaml for the aai repo and the yaml for the ci-management jjb yaml (from which all the jenkins jobs, nexus and nexus3 pushes will arrive)",
