        "timestamp": "2018-08-17 15:44:23.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 2: Code-Review-1\n\n(12 comments)\n\nGeneral comments:\n\n1. There should be NO references to the following strings anywhere in the codebase: \"AJSC\", \"ATT\" (or \"AT&T\"), \"OPENECOMP\". There maybe exceptional circumstances, but they should be removed where possible.\n\n2. version.properties file is missing in the root folder (see other projects for example)\n\nPlease see inline for specific comments.\n\nDue to the volume of code, there may be more changes required than those that I have pointed out. There should be another round of review (preferably by someone other than me) after the current issues are resolved.",
        "patchset_number": 2
